/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/

@[to_additive]
theorem smul_def [group G] [MulAction G β] (g : G) (f : «expr ↪ » α β) :
    «expr • » g f = f.trans (MulAction.toPerm g).to_embedding :=
  rfl
#align smul_def smul_def
smul_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ↪ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
@[simp, to_additive]
theorem smul_apply [group G] [MulAction G β] (g : G) (f : «expr ↪ » α β) (a : α) :
    («expr • » g f) a = «expr • » g (f a) :=
  rfl
#align smul_apply smul_apply
coe_smul:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ↪ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⇑ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
@[to_additive]
theorem coe_smul [group G] [MulAction G β] (g : G) (f : «expr ↪ » α β) : «expr⇑ » («expr • » g f) = «expr • » g f :=
  rfl
#align coe_smul coe_smul
